title: "Agent Security Harness"
abstract: "Multi-protocol agent security testing framework. 470+ executable security tests across 32 modules covering MCP, A2A, L402, and x402 wire protocols. Decision-layer attack scenarios, AIUC-1 pre-certification mapping, NIST AI 800-2 aligned."
